data.description: If you're looking for a charming home, you'll fall in love with this gem. This house offers a formal dining area and a spacious living room, perfect for entertaining guests. One room has been repurposed into a bedroom enclosed by an adorable barn door, but it can easily be converted back to its original use. There is a large master bedroom with walk-in closet with two additional bedrooms also including nice size closets. The property is located on a corner lot, and boasts a sizeable, level backyard that is enclosed by a chain-link fence. In addition, a detached one-stall garage is included. This home is conveniently located near shopping, schools, and the city park.
